{"tid":31484,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［星座撚］估星座有獎問答遊戲","createTime":"2016-12-09T16:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T10:35:07.000Z","uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf646c8353c0a22fbcecf970395bd9d2c3ef46f","tid":31484,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"見有巴打開post估星座玩得幾過癮<br />\n我又玩下先<br />\n不過我同佢唔同嘅呢，係我呢個遊戲有獎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n規則好簡單，由而家直至11/12/2016 00:00之前大家可以問問題，只要唔係直接問星座同月份日子果d我都盡量答大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果d幾月出世咩季節就唔使問喇。我唔會答嘅。<br />\n如果你淨係想玩下嘅，就咁留言估啦。<br />\n如果想要禮物嘅，就pm我留低你嘅聯絡方法。只要係我聽晚開估之前，最快估中（根據我inbox為準）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘅巴打/絲打，咁證明你都同我有緣丫，你會得到我親自準備嘅小禮物一份。但係，每人限估一個答案架咋，唔好諗住大包圍估哂12個就中硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n11/12/2016 00:00會開估同公布得獎者，機會難得，睇下你睇人眼光準唔準？"},{"pid":"023405bbc239b018cafce78ec3f02733ae4220e8","tid":31484,"uid":18048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:10:50.000Z","msg":"1定0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fb43122de23c08d1745f7d838cff78b37a3af6","tid":31484,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"星座撚對自己信既野咁冇信心架原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入黎用你地既星座論文推論啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0d012377a8faf6cb305ddf86ad8d3496d8c290","tid":31484,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad1f7197915cabedcb21f20d9bcafda479386ad6","tid":31484,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔瞭解星座既人先會叫人估或者去估人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一味淨信d大包圍「分析」